# Project Overview

Traffic congestion and accidents are common problems in many cities.

This project proposes a prototype intelligent traffic control system using VANET and IoT technologies.

The system detects nearby vehicles and obstacles using ultrasonic sensors and sends alerts to the driver.

Objectives:

- Detect nearby vehicles
- Measure safe distance
- Provide safety alerts
- Improve road safety

Outcome:

A working hardware prototype using Arduino and sensors capable of detecting obstacles and sending alerts.
